    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>A new horror/hidden-object game</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Keep a sharp eye out for changes in your environment, and mark them down with your handy reporting panel.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Watch out though! Let too many pile up and you'll have to give it another shot.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Can you last until the timer runs out?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3237050/extras/8621bc7f138910c5976f90b454f6a36a.poster.avif?t=1746036706\" width=720 height=404 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3237050/extras/8621bc7f138910c5976f90b454f6a36a.webm?t=1746036706\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3237050/extras/8621bc7f138910c5976f90b454f6a36a.mp4?t=1746036706\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>This game features</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >5 constantly changing levels to navigate:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A quaint new apartment.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A long abandoned diner.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A cabin in the woods.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A fun, family arcade.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A grand church.</p></li></ul></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Over 40 potential changes to see in every level. Making every run unique.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 2 gameplay modes: The standard fully lit mode, and a flashlight mode that removes all level lighting except your own light.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >2 difficulty modes that change how often the map changes.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3237050/extras/af88dd95169b1b2b2956f0a2b72dfaac.poster.avif?t=1746036706\" width=720 height=404 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3237050/extras/af88dd95169b1b2b2956f0a2b72dfaac.webm?t=1746036706\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3237050/extras/af88dd95169b1b2b2956f0a2b72dfaac.mp4?t=1746036706\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
